---
title: Cajun Chicken Salad with green veg and Greek style cheese
description: This salad is refreshing, crisp and comes with just a hint of Cajun spices. Featuring succulent chicken, crisp apple, fragrant toasted hazelnuts and tangy Greek style cheese, this is the perfect nourishing option for an easy weeknight meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W21_IE_IECC21821-3_Main_high-323fb0b9.jpg
